    "description": "Achilles Corporation engages in the manufacture and sale of shoes, plastic products, and industrial materials in Japan and internationally. It offers construction and civil engineering products, including heat insulation materials, interior materials, landscaping materials, plumbing material, and civil engineering materials; manufacturing and facilities products, such as films and sheets, rubberized fabrics, soft urethane foam, expanded polystyrene foam, and rim molding; and electrical machinery and electronics comprising anti-static products, packaging materials for wafers and electronic device, and conductive materials. The company also provides vehicle accessories, including synthetic and vinyl chloride leather, and laminated goods; and agriculture and livestock products, such as greenhouse horticulture materials and building materials for agriculture and livestock. In addition, it offers disaster prevention and lifesaving, as well as evacuation shelter support products; living and leisure products comprising household items and inflatable boats; and shoes under the MEDIFOAM, ALL DAY Walk, SYUNSOKU, Achilles SORBO, and MONTRRE brands. Achilles Corporation was incorporated in 1947 and is headquartered in Shinjuku, Japan."
